{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1081d8448a","title":"转发周小舟关于处理少数违法乱纪干部的意见的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1de1d504ac","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":17,"articleId":"1081d8448a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"2a01b5e7f7","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周小舟，当时任中共湖南省委第一书记。"},{"id":"1c99b74d4b","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"d0d36f6291","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周小舟1959年4月14日请中共湖北省委第一书记王任重、浙江省委第一书记江华转毛泽东的报告。报告说，我们日内即将召开地委书记会议，讨论执行上海会议关于人民公社的十三条指示。会后即可分批召开县的六级干部会议。对于少数递法乱纪的干部，完全应该依法严肃惩处，现已处理了少数分子。但是我们认为不必集中在一次会议上处理，而以实事求是精神调查清楚后随即处理比较适当。至于某些不称职的于部，在公社代表大会上应该尽量改选掉。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2fd89f4082","type":"title","text":"转发周小舟\"关于处理少数违法乱纪干部的意见的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a"},{"id":"2a01b5e7f7","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆?","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a"},{"id":"1c99b74d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请转各地方同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a"},{"id":"d0d36f6291","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a"},{"id":"40758744ee","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a"}],"page":{"id":"811a4f379f","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"1081d8448a","sta